title: NFC Free Agency Grades: Tom Brady's worth to the Bucs, Panthers release Cam Newton (Football 3/25)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Jonathan Jones to grade the free agency moves of all NFC Teams with an extra focus on the Bucs, who introduced Tom Brady on Tuesday (10:55) and the Panthers, who released Cam Newton (20:35). The guys also issue grades for the Cowboys (31:15), Giants (34:30), Eagles (36:00), Redskins (37:40), Vikings (39:45), Bears (46:50), Packers (49:00) , Lions (50:15), Falcons (52:45), Saints (54:30), Cardinals (56:00), Rams (58:00), 49ers (59:15) and Seahawks (1:01:00).

Pick Six' is available on Apple Podcasts, Spotify, Stitcher, Castbox, Bullhorn and wherever else you listen to podcasts.
